{"type": "article", "id": 9672, "title": "“Weaver” 茶具系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-18T07:23:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235637eTPqRSrmWZInLtuG.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t台湾设计公司 TOAST Living 推出了一款叫做 “Weaver” 的茶具系列，包括两个冲茶器和一个茶叶罐，分别有精铜色和不锈钢两种颜色。器皿们的外部看似随意的纹理模仿的其实是传统的竹编织工艺，力求提升人们的用茶体验。TOAST Living 公司一直专注于各种极简家庭用品设计，<a href=\"http://www.toastliving.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是他们的官方网站</a>，感兴趣的话可以点击查看。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235636gr5HGJMVK9dxsbDW.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052356369VRBzGqgrPZw0mFL.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235637140qaOuEd2PK39Lx.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}